                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-12-29</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">尼采哲学与西方哲学之脉络梳理得很清楚。永恒轮回太科幻。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1078101047">
